<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Support - RPay</title>
    <link href="/css/style.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="nav-brand">
                <i class="fas fa-qrcode"></i> RPay
            </div>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/">Home</a>
                <a href="/docs">Docs</a>
                <% if (user) { %>
                    <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
                    <a href="/logout">Logout</a>
                <% } else { %>
                    <a href="/auth/login">Login</a>
                    <a href="/auth/register">Register</a>
                <% } %>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <div class="card">
            <h2 class="card-title">Support Center</h2>
            <p>Jika Anda mengalami masalah atau memiliki pertanyaan, jangan ragu untuk menghubungi kami.</p>

            <div class="feature-card" style="margin: 20px 0;">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> Email Support</h3>
                <p>support@rpay.xyz</p>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card" style="margin: 20px 0;">
                <h3><i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> WhatsApp Support</h3>
                <p>+62 895-2503-6410</p>
                <a href="https://wa.me/6289525036410" class="btn btn-success" target="_blank">
                    <i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> Chat via WhatsApp
                </a>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-card" style="margin: 20px 0;">
                <h3><i class="fas fa-question-circle"></i> FAQ</h3>
                <p><strong>Q: Berapa lama verifikasi API Key?</strong></p>
                <p>A: Biasanya dalam 1x24 jam.</p>
                <p><strong>Q: Apakah ada biaya bulanan?</strong></p>
                <p>A: Tidak, hanya biaya transaksi 1.4% + Rp 300.</p>
                <p><strong>Q: Bagaimana cara pencairan saldo?</strong></p>
                <p>A: Bisa dilakukan melalui dashboard, akan dihubungi admin via WhatsApp.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
